Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:10.06,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫住手 那不是古拉多斯军 可能是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.91,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,雷兹纳 变成蓝色的火焰燃烧起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:51.94,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那看起来好像是隐藏的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.97,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,爆发开来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:02:00.77,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,然后 对那个人来说却是个令人悲伤的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.45,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:04.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:10.18,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:19.24,Layzner_Title,Eiji,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}月球！请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:27.74,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,好怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.72,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,美军基地那没有回应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.58,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对 虽然我已照你的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:36.49,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,用宇宙救助法所规定的紧急频道呼叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.30,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,继续 不能灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:44.28,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这样下去 我们要降落的话 会先被某一边击落的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:48.54,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我知道 这航天飞机要是地球的东西就没问题对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.47,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,亚瑟 再休息一下就跟罗安换班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.87,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.60,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,他一直把自己封闭起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.50,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,由当时情况来判断 那个人一定死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.87,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对他的打击一定很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.24,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,吃完这个 我就去看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.89,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,就算英二不想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.98,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,但他的确是杀了他的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:22.31,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,英二也因此 一直把自己封闭在雷兹纳里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.95,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.83,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,要怎么安慰他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.45,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.42,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,前辈 那时你真的躲不开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.92,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.13,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这真的是宿命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.34,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我真的不想对你开枪  可是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.45,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,啊 和古斯特罗打的时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.32,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,让我看一下战斗记录
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.02,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已加载
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:10.42,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这波动是我被击中前产生的 并没有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.23,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.13,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:32.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.98,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么只有这时候影像没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,为什么只有这时有异常的能源显示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.98,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,雷 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:58.06,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,为什么最后射主炮时有异常的能源显示 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.85,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,无法解释
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.92,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.49,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,能源正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.75,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,能源残量如显示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.92,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,给我老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.56,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,能源正常 不能理解你问题的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.25,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,拜托 给我老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.20,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,不明白你问题的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.01,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:18.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,一定有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.11,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,雷兹纳里一定有什么 我不知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.80,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 要不要出来喝个汤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.46,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.47,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我知道你现在想一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.95,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可是跟大家一起比较能平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.74,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,谢谢 等我平静下再出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.99,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那就好 我只是有点担心你 那等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.32,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,让我看打倒古斯特罗时的战斗记录
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:46.82,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已加载
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.50,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,是吗 盖尔也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:57.10,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我一定会帮他报仇 请让我替他报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.49,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,请允许我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.49,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.15,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,祖鲁副官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.57,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,改变航道 回来这里与我们汇合 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.92,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,你说要改变航道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.77,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,我们已派别动队实行新计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.68,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,现在一切顺利 你这一去会打乱计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.25,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,绝对不准你去月球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.15,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,那么至少让我找回盖尔中尉的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.18,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,那只是浪费时间 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:30.40,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,拜托您 请叫古雷斯科陛下 至少让我做完这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:34.45,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,在宇宙死的人 就让宇宙做他的墓场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.87,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.33,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,就这样 快点行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.14,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,请等一下 副官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.30,Default_Sub,Officer,0,0,0,,要修正航道了 请待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.51,Default_Sub,Officer,0,0,0,,要修正航道了 请待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.68,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不行 苏联军也没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.25,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,还有五分钟着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:17.35,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这样也没办法了 只好由我们单方联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.43,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,把路线打开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.49,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.94,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,通知月球基地和苏联军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.66,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我是隶属联合国宇宙局的伊丽莎白·克蕾布里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:29.58,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我们将要降落在联合国的月球基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.30,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,虽然是坐没有看过的舰艇来的 但这是紧急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.82,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,上面有地球人 请不要攻击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.15,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,请不要攻击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.78,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,有传到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:49.21,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,还有四分钟着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.84,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,每一个人都沉浸在一片不安的氛围中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:59.64,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,一种想告诉大家的事情 却无法说出口的心情中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:03.04,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,让我们感到十分的烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.59,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.55,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,已经无法更改航道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:11.18,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这下只有强行降落在联合国月球基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:14.48,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,为什么 联合国基地不回答我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.17,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,现在多想也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:20.82,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我们只好相信 他们有收到我们的通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:23.39,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,如果他们没收到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.25,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,往好的方面想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.37,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这里不是火星是月球耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.05,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,是有三万地球人住的月球 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:36.69,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,如西蒙尼所说 我们要相信他们一定有收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.30,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对啊 与其怀疑不如相信比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.72,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,没错 降落的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.39,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,好想马上就去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:49.92,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,那我们去那里好吗 就是训练场附近的牛排屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.86,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那之前先让我洗个热水澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.96,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,你还真爱干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.20,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对啊 大概没人比我更爱干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.34,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不过你还真忍得住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.64,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们好几天没洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:07.85,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我的内裤就一直湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.58,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,亚瑟 在你面前的是淑女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.57,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,真不知道他家的大人是怎么教他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,果然那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:34.44,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,果然好怪 怎么想都好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:39.43,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,就算雷说的是真的 可是这雷兹纳一定有什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.29,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,英二 大卫 准备降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.41,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.40,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我在贝布鲁上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.41,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:48.74,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我跟你换
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:49.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:51.95,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,快到了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.96,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,两分钟后降落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.57,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,坐那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.36,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不 我去跟亚瑟换
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.66,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,英二 人生难免有难以预料的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.27,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,有时结果说不定还很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.23,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我来跟你换
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.80,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是啊 由你来我就更安心了 那拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.92,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫在贝布鲁上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.62,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,看到你这样子我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:23.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.32,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,只是有你坐在旁边我才安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:31.89,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,谢谢你 罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.00,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,准备着陆 请确认主灯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.39,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.39,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,切换主控制系统 请确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:38.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.52,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,启动窗外视窗模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.59,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,确认 没有异状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:50.83,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,离着陆时间还有34秒...33...32...31...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:55.89,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,30... 29... 28... 27... 26...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:11:00.87,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,25... 24... 23... 22... 21...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:05.91,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,20... 19... 18... 17... 16...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:10.74,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,15... 14... 13... 12... 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:15.62,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,10... 09... 08... 07... 06...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:21.42,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,05... 04... 03... 02... 01...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.58,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\bord1\b0\3c&HDFDEEA&\c&HD4D9E4&\pos(720,1040)}联合国宇宙局 月球基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.15,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,怎么有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.52,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 请来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里 也被古拉多斯军摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:45.63,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,这里是月球啊 这里有军队 和火星不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.80,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.87,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.04,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,说不定苏联军和美军也被
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.84,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那我们就这样去地球吧 那样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:03.89,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,搞不好还有跟我们一样存活着的地球人 躲在哪里避难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.59,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你的意思是要下去是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:09.27,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,在这里我们无法知道外面的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.98,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我用贝布鲁去看看外面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.43,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.19,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:18.72,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你留下来 要留一架SPT才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.53,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 我跟英二去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.29,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.35,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么说我可在这生活过半年呢 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:30.94,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,说的也是 那拜托你了 我们留在这用航天飞机做后援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.81,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,知道了 走吧 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.66,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:55.91,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这里有70%的设施都在地下 住人的地方也是在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:56.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:57.97,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.11,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.87,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,跟火星的样子又完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.31,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,先别说这个 大家都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.10,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,前面有以前我们住的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:38.74,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,本来就在这前面的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.14,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那你说的宿舍就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.04,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:52.55,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,为什么我们看到的景色都是这种样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.22,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,想洗澡都只是个梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.98,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你还想着这种无聊的事情啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:06.44,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,进去吧 要等大卫的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.45,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我们以前住的宿舍也变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.98,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,真令人感到绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.97,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:55.48,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,资料信息 攻击武器识别 巴尔干炮一门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还有自动型火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.46,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:04.73,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,住手 大卫 这不是古拉多斯军 可能是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.16,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:16.93,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,听好了 我们不攻击的话就要被敌人干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.68,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,他们来了 不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.31,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要开枪 我们不会攻击你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:25.98,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:32.36,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我是地球人 停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.77,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,我们不会上当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.92,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,怎么了 快回自己的岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.88,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.28,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要开枪 我要下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.06,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫他们好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.08,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,是我 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.71,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,你们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.78,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我已经离开了主广场 现在在往北边的广场的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:33.55,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.28,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,找到一名美军的飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.47,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,剩下还有几人 但能确认的只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.41,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,他们都不问清楚就攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.19,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,别搞错了 是美军的士兵对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.26,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,看来他好像受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.59,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我虽然接近他 但却无法和他沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.67,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我想确认这基地的通信频道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.91,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,调到F208 426.7Hz就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.62,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我也去 从这走去还不到一公里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.86,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,听好了 别看丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:02.89,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.45,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.11,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,现在还不知道情形 听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:11.42,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,知道详细情形就会叫大家 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.56,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们会在这等你的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.09,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.10,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,为什么擅自离开岗位 你们想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.32,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,快把枪捡起来 继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.02,Default_Sub,Joy,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.79,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,把枪给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.34,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,帮我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:59.21,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要开枪 我已确认你的美军身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我也是美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:04.61,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我叫大卫·鲁瑟福特 现在坐在这东西上是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.66,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我现在要下来了 不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.21,Default_Sub,Joy,0,0,0,,他下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.11,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,只有一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.57,Default_Sub,Joy,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:14.63,Default_Sub,Joy,0,0,0,,他把手举起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.88,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,他手上有武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:17.87,Default_Sub,Joy,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.94,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,你从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:23.21,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,火星 我是从火星逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.63,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,从火星 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.46,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们是体验学校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:41.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.87,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,坐在另一架机器人上的也是学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:45.74,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.52,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:49.18,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不过他也是同伴 请把枪收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:51.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,然后我再告诉你详情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.13,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,听你说了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.97,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,可对外星人的感觉还是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.35,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,但想不到月球也变这样了 那其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.20,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,我是因为解体而变这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.47,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,其他的部队到哪里了我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.71,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那这些小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.84,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,好像是从学校里出来避难的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.64,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,连名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:27.84,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,你们的事 只花两三分钟的解释 很难让我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:32.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道 可是他说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:36.26,Default_Sub,?,0,0,0,,骗人 就算是混血 但外星人一定不可能长这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.68,Default_Sub,?,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得 长的和我们一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.62,Default_Sub,?,0,0,0,,跟电影里的外星人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.04,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:47.99,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.66,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:53.68,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,古雷特 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:56.25,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,是伊丽莎白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:01.60,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,真的是你 但你怎么会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.51,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这真是一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:06.06,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,那之后我打了好多次电话给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.57,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,那事先别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.10,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,你好自私
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.63,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,还比不上你 古雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:43.70,Default_Sub,Kids,0,0,0,,来了 他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.03,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.68,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,安静 大家安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:49.94,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,好像有什么响声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:50.91,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.65,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.39,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,你也拿把枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.25,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你说话的口气还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.63,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,那是为了要活着离开这里啊  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.17,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,古雷特 你连小孩子都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:06.00,Default_Sub,Clayton,0,0,0,,小孩子又怎样 小孩子他们也很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.06,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,请你说明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.28,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,先对付眼前敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:25.04,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,警告 未确认物接近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.60,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,资料不足 无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.63,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,请重新部署
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:33.99,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,一定是敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:38.42,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,真令人无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:42.82,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,还差一点就到地球的月球上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:49.16,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我们看到了比在火星上更可怕的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.89,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 那时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:00.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这时候不要说以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:02.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 你说得对
